        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer57307251" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1760542100222656268"> True testimony of redemption. God&apos;s Angel appeared to me and began his message with &quot;I am an Angel of David&apos;s Lord. I am Raphael. I come in the name of the Healer.&quot; <br/> I knew nothing about God&apos;s angel before this. I discovered that Raphael means &quot;Healer&quot;. And of course Christ is our Healer. The Angel&apos;s words and messages to me were so layered with deep meanings.<br/> God&apos;s ways are above our ways. He will bring us out of our ignorance into the Glory with Him if we only have faith to believe that He IS</span>
  <span id="freeText1760542100222656268" style="display:none"> True testimony of redemption. God's Angel appeared to me and began his message with "I am an Angel of David's Lord. I am Raphael. I come in the name of the Healer." <br /> I knew nothing about God's angel before this. I discovered that Raphael means "Healer". And of course Christ is our Healer. The Angel's words and messages to me were so layered with deep meanings.<br /> God's ways are above our ways. He will bring us out of our ignorance into the Glory with Him if we only have faith to believe that He IS.<br /> From the experiences that the Lord allowed me, I learned a whole lot more about the nature of God and what the truth about Love is. <br />As the Author of this book, I am truly grateful that the Lord Christ Jesus talks to me, and allows me into the Most High realm that a believer in Christ Jesus as Savior can have the priviledge to experience. I know what the Lord is doing in my life is the most amazing and totally unheard of things, I know that I've been called a mystic, and a prophet. I just consider myself a highly favored child of God like any of us is who truly accepts Jesus as Savior and who truly goes through the gates that the Holy Spirit transports the believer through. <br /> I know that each person has their own experiences, mine are chronicled here in Communions With Christ to tell my testimony. The Bible says that the sharing of our true testimonies is for the building up of faith. Believe me, my faith is unalterable after having His angel appear to me and then Himself in Kindness appearing within my spirit so intensely - the revelations have anchored my faith and made whole my life in Him. I learned that God is real and the Christian Bible says Truth ... Sharon</span>
