  <span id="freeText2407973238295024278" style="display:none"> Except for the Bible, this book, "Communions With Christ" is the greatest harmonious tune to ever pull at my spirit's heartstrings. There abides a hunger, a craving, an incredible awakening in these words from Christ, our Lord, written through this author.<br /> As I read, there remains no doubt in my mind that these messages are for Christian growth, healing and fullness in Him, our King. In each reading there is more to ponder, glean, and to realize into our very souls/spirits.<br /> Praise be to this author who, in spite of overwhelming personal hardships, accepted the invitation of Christ to HEAR His Words, accept them, and then through obedience, deep emotions, and joyful love and faithfulness wrote this book with Christ's exact words that we might be filled.<br /> A MUST READ for all Christians and all who desire peace, joy and spiritual growth to fill their lives. To me, Christ is telling us that it is time to renew our faith and draw closer to Him. <br /> My undying thanks to Sharon Ellis for this Hope and JOy in Christ.<br /> Patricia L. Moore</span>
