<span id="freeTextContainer17426697865019684015">This book was put in my path for a reason. I had another book in my hand to buy and then my hands found this sitting on a table before checkout. I put the other one down and bought it. The autograph inside says &quot;Obey God&apos;s Requests.&quot; I too have very peculiar things happen to me as well. As I was reading a few minutes ago I told God I wanted to meet this interesting writer and asked if that was possible...then my laptop which was closed and untouched burst out into a song from Addison Road just f</span>
  <span id="freeText17426697865019684015" style="display:none">This book was put in my path for a reason. I had another book in my hand to buy and then my hands found this sitting on a table before checkout. I put the other one down and bought it. The autograph inside says "Obey God's Requests." I too have very peculiar things happen to me as well. As I was reading a few minutes ago I told God I wanted to meet this interesting writer and asked if that was possible...then my laptop which was closed and untouched burst out into a song from Addison Road just for 2 seconds. I got chills. So maybe our paths will cross one day :) Love this book and can't wait to keep reading it. <br />~In His Name<br />Ashley</span>
