  <span id="freeText11849998090197561382" style="display:none">"SEEING THE LIBERTY, The Journey Of Eve's Daughter" by Sharon Roni Ellis &gt; **A Memoir**<br />**Sharon has seen angels her whole life. Why? <br /> This soul penetrating true story of uncommon things occurring as adversity giving way to transforming redemption -leaves you feeling emotionally wrung out, stunned, inspired, and wanting more.<br /> Spanning six decades, with all the walls down, Sharon reveals the bare gut wrenching truth of her passage through terror into glorious meeting and speaking with God. <br /> Between the beginning and the end of this masterpiece lies a treasure so profound that your spirit will realize only God could have thought all these things up, or caused these true events to happen! Only God can supernaturally do what is documented in these pages of surprising depth. <br /> A stunning revelation of the love of the Father &amp; His huge message to us now.<br /> SEEING THE LIBERTY is an extraordinary explanation of the life and journey of a true Christian mystic who has been given by God the destiny of understanding the Mystical Marriage to Christ in direct awareness of God, and who has been chosen and commissioned by the Grace of God to tell the pathway of struggle that leads her to His Heart. **<br /><br />"COMMUNIONS WITH CHRIST, Mystical Revelations Of Infinite Wisdom From Our Creator" by Sharon Ellis. Amazing True Story! <br />find at <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.amazon.com/communions-christ-sharon-ellis/dp/1606478893">http://www.amazon.com/communions-chri...</a><br /><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.Lifewaystores.com/lwstore/dept.asp?dept=abk">http://www.Lifewaystores.com/lwstore/...</a><br /> Barnes&amp;Noble.com Target.com <br />GoHastings.com has some good reduced special prices!<br />And From out of my ignorance God just came down from heaven and targeted me for Himself. I'm so glad that He calls us, each individually. My wake up call was in the frightening yet amazing appearance of a Holy Angel appearing to me - right in the middle of Vista Ridge Mall in Lewisville, Texas, under the huge glass doam in the atruim.<br />I saw the heavenly Real ArchAngel of the Lord, not the stuff people make up stories about, but the Real Thing. The Angel said, "I am Raphael. I come in the Name of the Healer. I am an Angel of David's Lord."<br />I was just an ordinary person, filled with fears and phobias, but the angel figured he would tell me his message. Why me? and then the most tremendous supernatural things began to happen to me, and to people I came into contact with. How does a person deal with this? <br /><br />&gt;BOOK SIGNING TOUR--- June 19 Friday 1PM to 5PM, Hastings Bookstore 2306 S. Jefferson, MOUNT PLEASANT, TX 75455. --- JULY 11 Saturday Hastings Bookstore 12 Noon to 4PM 2114 Texoma Pkwy, SHERMAN, TX --- July 18 Saturday 2PM to 8PM Barnes &amp; Noble Sundance Square 401 Commerce St. FORT WORTH, TX 76102 -- JULY 24 Friday 3PM to 6PM, Hastings Bookstore 651 N. Business IH35, NEW BRANFELS, TX. 78130, --- JULY 25 12 Noon to 4PM, Hastings Bookstore 917 s. Hwy. 80 SAN MARCOS, TX 78666. --- August 22 Saturday 12Noon to 4PM Hastings Bookstore DENTON, Tx. --- September 25, Friday 2PM to 6PM, Hastings Bookstore 4501 North St., NACOGDOCHES TX. 75961. -- September 26, 12 Noon to 4PM Barnes &amp; Noble 4916 South Broadway, TYLER TX. 75703, --- October 3, Saturday 12 Noon to 4PM, Barnes &amp; Noble Parks at ARLINGTON, 38815 S. Cooper, ARLINGTON TX, 76015. --- October 17, Saturday 12 Noon to 4 PM, The Scroll Christian Bookstore, 2752 E. Fifth St. TYLER TX, 75701. --- November 14, Saturday, 12 Noon to 4PM, Barnes &amp; Noble Firewheel Mall, 190 Cedar Sage Dr. GARLAND TX. 75040. --- November 21 Saturday, 12 Noon to 4 PM, Barnes &amp; Noble Hulen, 4801 Overton Ridge Blvd., FORT WORTH TX, 76132.</span>
